## ModifyFilesResponse.newStoreVersion property

The new version of the store after the modifcations have been made.

**Signature:**

```typescript
newStoreVersion: bigint;
```

## Remarks

If [ModifyFilesRequest.allowUnchanged](./hub.modifyfilesrequest.allowunchanged.md) was `true`<!-- -->, this will be the existing store version if no changes were made.
